# Apps Matrix

Only used in monorepos that ship multiple apps from the same codebase (e.g.
an admin + a client portal). Single-app projects can delete this file.

The agent reads this matrix **before** choosing a pattern or import — every
row represents a behavioral difference the agent must respect when touching
files under the named app path.

## Matrix

Replace `<fill>` cells. Add / remove columns as your project needs.

