## Cross-app rules

- Apps MUST NOT import from each other. Shared logic goes in `{{UI_PACKAGE}}` or
  sibling shared workspace packages.
- When a task spans both apps, open two plans — one per app — and verify each
  separately.
- Do not mix `<app-a>` authorization / error patterns into `<app-b>` pages
  (or vice-versa).

## How the agent uses this

1. Resolve target app from the trigger (e.g. `TC target=apps/admin/...`) or
   from the file path the user names.
2. Look up the row that matches the behavior in question.
3. If two apps differ, pick the app's value — never average or invent a
   hybrid.
